    "The review revealed a growing interest in this field, as evidenced by the increasing number of publications over the years.",
    "Traditional machine learning models like Logistic Regression, Random Forest, and Support Vector Machine (SVM) remain prevalent, but there is a notable rise in the use of deep learning models such as Multilayer Perceptrons (MLP) and Long Short-Term Memory (LSTM) networks.",
    "Among the most explored algorithms, Graph Convolutional Networks (GCNs) stand out for their effectiveness in analyzing graph-structured data, particularly in the context of cryptocurrency transaction networks.",
